  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "🚚 PART-TIME DELIVERY DRIVER (B2B/B2C LAST-MILE)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for part-time delivery drivers to join our growing last-mile logistics company, Draft Logistics Pte Ltd.</p><p>What we offer:</p><p>2-3 day work week (Monday to Saturday)</p><p>Delivery hours: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM (or when deliveries done for the day)</p><p>Performance-based bonus for exceeding KPIs</p><p>Job Scope:</p><p>Assist in loading and unloading</p><p>Ensure safe and timely delivery of items</p><p>Collection of receipts and payments if any</p><p>Meeting delivery deadline</p><p>Ad Hoc duties as per assigned by Manager</p><p>Driver Requirements:</p><p>Min 1-2 years of working experience</p><p>Have own vehicle to do deliveries</p><p>Good driving record</p><p>Valid Class 3/ 3A Driving Licence (minimum 2 years)</p><p>Responsible, Courteous, Punctual, Independent and Familiar with Singapore road</p><p>Must be Physically fit</p><p>Salary & Benefits:</p><p>Basic salary: S$8-15/location (depending on urgency)</p><p>Performance bonus available</p><p>Job Type: Part time</p><p>Work Location: Central</p><p>Interested applicants, please WhatsApp +65 89698549 or email admin@draft-logistics.com with your name, driving experience, and availability. Thank you and hope to connect with you!</p><p>Draft Logistics – Singapore</p>",
